i did a video awhile ago talking about how awkward my time in primary school, was and well?...
Turns out my high school years were not all that much better. I've had lots of embarrassing moments throughout my life
And high school in particular, was no exception.
Let me tell you some of them.
You know how everyone has those nightmares in school that maybe one day they might show up to class wearing really
Weird clothes or just their underwear or even no clothes at all? (wat ._.)
Yeah, well...
Something like that kind of happened to me once. One time at school, my class decided that they
wanted to have a Pajama Day (oooo :D) since i was so shy back then, i wasn't really sure if i wanted to come to school in my pajamas
It seemed kind of embarrassing but
My friend insisted that i should do it just because if i didn't id be only one in the entire class to not be wearing pajamas (poor wolfy ;-;)
I really didn't want to stand out like that and be the boring one of the year
the next morning
I put on my shoes and i walked to school in my pajamas :3
it felt really Awkward to be walking around outside in my pajamas i felt like everybody, was staring at me i also didn't know
If the people from other classes knew, about  pajama, day, since it was only my year that
Was doing it. When i got to school i kind of waited out of sight for everybody else to go inside so i could sneak
In with as little people seeing
Me as possible. I was moving down those hallways like a ninja >:3
avoiding every single person that I saw.
I knew I'd be fine once i was in the classroom with all of the other people in their pajamas
Then i go to my classroom and i ran straight inside but then i realized that, something
Wasn't right. I looked around and realized that not one other person
Was wearing their pajamas. i stood there frozen not knowing, what to do, while everybody
Else just started to laugh at me. T^T .It turns out that everybody decided to back out
the pajama
Day at the last minute and nobody told me
So i was the only one who turned up to school in my pajamas and to make it worse i remember
My pajamas were really dorky looking as, well and that's not even where that story ends because on the same
Day since i was embarrassed about being the only one wearing pajamas i wanted to get changed as soon as i could.
The bathroom was full of people. The only stall available, was the one at the end with the broken lock.
I didn't really want to use that one but since i didn't want to stand in the middle of a
busy
Bathroom in my pajamas i decided to just go in there anyway i started to get changed and everything was fine until
i noticed footsteps coming towards this side of the
Bathroom then all of a sudden the door swung open and my worst fears have been realized
A girl, was standing in the door looking right at me
I didn't know
what to do i started to freak out and she just ran away i was so embarrassed i wanted to cry i
Hurried up to get the rest of my clothes on i rushed out of that bathroom
As fast as i could >.<
Just hoping that nobody else had seen what happened as soon as i got to my next lesson
And thought that i could finally forget about it i realized that the exact, same girl, was in this class i could
Feel her staring at me for the entire lesson
And that's not even where the embarrassing stories end do any of you remember heely's?
I used to love them it was always so much fun to skate around on them everywhere i went i did have a
Few bad falls in them though, like this one time in P.E where i don't remember exactly what we were doing
but we were coming up one by one to the front of the class to do some kind of jumps
I was wearing my heely's that day
But it was the kind where the wheel was kind of tucked in neatly to the shoes so you could
Still use them as ordinary runners
They did make all the noise when i ran in them though
anyway
When it was my turn to go up to the front of the class i was feeling
Confident because of i thought i was actually pretty good at doing different kinds of jumps
So i bent down and jumped up as high as i could
And then went for the perfect landing but as soon as i hit the ground i felt

my
feet slip from underneath of me because of four wheels and my shoes and i had what was probably the most dramatic
Looking fall anyone in my class had ever seen
Right down onto my butt
just picture a cartoon character slipping on a banana peel because that's probably exactly
What i looked like. I remember it would hurt to sit down for like two, days after that happened as well.
I also, never wore my heely's on p.e days ever again
